<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<title>Skalver | Dashboard</title>
		<meta name="description" content="Dashboard of Skalver web app"/>
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"/>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
	</head>

	<body id="page_container_login" class="d-flex h-100">
        <div class="d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">

            <header class="p-2">
                <div class="text-light d-flex align-items-center justify-content-around">
                    <div>
                        <h1 class="h3 mb-1">Skalver</h1>
                        <p class="mb-1"><em>The distraction free worldbuilding tool</em></p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <a class="btn btn-outline-light" href="/about">About</a>
                        <a class="btn btn-outline-light" href="/feedback">Feedback</a>
                        <a class="btn btn-outline-warning" href="/register">Register</a>
                    </div>
            </header>

            <main class="px-3 w-100 container">
                <div class="row justify-content-center">
                    <div class="col-5">
                        <form action="/login" method="POST">
                            <div class="form-floating mb-3">
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="floatingInput"
                                placeholder="Username" name="username" required>
                                <label for="floatingInput">Username</label>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-floating mb-3">
                                <input type="password" class="form-control" id="floatingPassword"
                                placeholder="Password" name="password" required>
                                <label for="floatingPassword">Password</label>
                            </div>
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary w-100">Login</button>
                        </form> 
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-3 text-light">
                        <p>Welcome to Skalver - a minimalist digital library for
                        writers and worldbuilders who want a distraction free
                        environment to gather and structure documents, notes and
                        stories.</p>
                        <p>Skalver aims to be the best of both worlds in terms of
                        ease of use and organization, to keep as little as possible
                        standing between you and what really matters: just writing.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </main>

            <footer class="text-light row p-2 w-100">
                <div class="col-8">
                    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit.
                    Voluptates eos omnis pariatur excepturi, libero odio, ea
                    fuga voluptas vitae tempora, aliquam commodi tempore maxime
                    facilis?</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-4">
                    <h5>Follow the project on GitHub</h5>
                    <a href="www.github.com/oxifinch/skalver">Skalver on GitHub</a>
                </div>
            </footer>

        </div>
	</body>
</html>

